464
00:27:12,850 --> 00:27:14,630
and incredible verse

465
00:27:14,630 --> 00:27:15,870
from Romans chapter 8

466
00:27:15,870 --> 00:27:18,420
remember this church

467
00:27:18,420 --> 00:27:21,950
Paul writes can anything ever

468
00:27:21,950 --> 00:27:23,630
