469
00:27:23,630 --> 00:27:27,160
does it mean he no longer loves

470
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:29,120
us if we have trouble

471
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:35,620
or calamity, or are persecuted, or are hungry, or cold, or in dark, or danger, or threatened with

472
00:27:35,620 --> 00:27:42,480
death. Even the scriptures say, for your sake we are killed every day. We're being slaughtered like

473
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:49,020
sheep. No, despite all these things, overwhelming victory is ours through Christ who loved us.

474
00:27:51,080 --> 00:27:58,380
And I'm convinced, he writes, that nothing can ever separate us from his love. Death can't. Life can't.

475
00:27:59,330 --> 00:28:02,170
The angels can't, and the demons can't.

476
00:28:02,230 --> 00:28:05,370
Our fears for today, our worries about tomorrow,

477
00:28:05,370 --> 00:28:09,050
and even the powers of hell cannot keep God's love away.

478
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:13,620
Whether we're high above the sky or in the deepest ocean,

479
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:18,420
nothing in all creation will ever be able to separate us

480
00:28:18,420 --> 00:28:23,000
from the love of God that is revealed in Christ Jesus, our Lord.

481
00:28:24,230 --> 00:28:28,050
Church, let that one just percolate down into your soul.

482
00:28:28,050 --> 00:28:30,410
nothing can separate you

483
00:28:30,410 --> 00:28:31,590
from the love of God

484
00:28:31,590 --> 00:28:33,830
and if you are in Jesus

485
00:28:33,830 --> 00:28:35,770
the fear of death, the sting of death

486
00:28:35,770 --> 00:28:37,790
nothing can separate you

487
00:28:37,790 --> 00:28:39,210
from the love of God

488
00:28:39,210 --> 00:28:41,560
you have hope church

489
00:28:41,560 --> 00:28:46,390
we have hope because Jesus loves you

490
00:28:46,390 --> 00:28:48,580
he's got a hope for you

491
00:28:48,580 --> 00:28:50,860
and no matter what this world brings

492
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:52,620
whatever our lives bring there is hope

493
00:28:52,620 --> 00:28:54,330
for the end

494
00:28:54,330 --> 00:28:55,950
and for life eternal

495
00:28:55,950 --> 00:28:58,240
and that power begins now

496
00:28:58,240 --> 00:29:01,490
and nothing can separate you from his love

497
00:29:01,490 --> 00:29:08,730
don't ever forget that no matter what you face nothing can separate you from his love let us

