506
00:29:50,990 --> 00:29:54,410
and bless others who need to hear that hope,

507
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:56,540
to experience that hope.

508
00:29:57,000 --> 00:29:59,640
May we be the ambassadors of the hope

509
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:01,680
that we have in Jesus Christ.

510
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:05,300
And Lord, now as we come and gather around your table,

511
00:30:06,130 --> 00:30:07,290
may you lift our heads

512
00:30:07,290 --> 00:30:10,190
and may we celebrate the hope that we have

513
00:30:10,190 --> 00:30:12,870
because of what Jesus did for us.

514
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:16,280
And we thank you and we praise you in Jesus' name.

515
00:30:17,370 --> 00:30:17,650
Amen.

